code: @Override protected Aggregator doCreateInternal(ValuesSource.Numeric valuesSource, Aggregator parent, boolean collectsFromSingleBucket, List<PipelineAggregator> pipelineAggregators, Map<String, Object> metaData) throws IOException {     if (collectsFromSingleBucket == false) {         return asMultiBucketAggregator(this, context, parent).     }     return createAggregator(valuesSource, parent, pipelineAggregators, metaData). }

private Aggregator createAggregator(ValuesSource.Numeric valuesSource, Aggregator parent, List<PipelineAggregator> pipelineAggregators, Map<String, Object> metaData) throws IOException {     return new HistogramAggregator(name, factories, interval, offset, order, keyed, minDocCount, minBound, maxBound, valuesSource, config.format(), context, parent, pipelineAggregators, metaData). }

@Override protected Aggregator createUnmapped(Aggregator parent, List<PipelineAggregator> pipelineAggregators, Map<String, Object> metaData) throws IOException {     return createAggregator(null, parent, pipelineAggregators, metaData). }
